{
  "page": "Hukko",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Hukko</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Hugor_of_the_Hill\" title=\"Hugor of the Hill\">Hugor of the Hill</a> <small>(speculated)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hukko</b> is the name given by <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentoshi</a> singers to a legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> hero.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hukko&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to legend he slew the <a href=\"/index.php/Swan_maidens\" title=\"Swan maidens\">swan maidens</a>, who lured travelers to their deaths in the <a href=\"/index.php/Velvet_Hills\" title=\"Velvet Hills\">Velvet Hills</a>; though not for their crimes but as sacrifices to <a href=\"/index.php/The_Seven\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Seven\">the Seven</a>. Some <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maesters</a> note \"Hukko\" may be a rendering of the name of <a href=\"/index.php/Hugor_of_the_Hill\" title=\"Hugor of the Hill\">Hugor</a>, the first king of the Andals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hukko&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Arrival of the Andals.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403154929\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.091 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.305 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 391/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10370/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3096/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 482/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 707/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  296.